CREATE TABLE [umbracoUser] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[userDisabled] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_userDisabled] DEFAULT ('0'),
[userNoConsole] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_userNoConsole] DEFAULT ('0'),
[userName] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[userLogin] NVARCHAR(125) NOT NULL,
[userPassword] NVARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
[passwordConfig] NVARCHAR(500) NULL,
[userEmail] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[userLanguage] NVARCHAR(10) NULL,
[securityStampToken] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[failedLoginAttempts] INTEGER NULL,
[lastLockoutDate] DATETIME NULL,
[lastPasswordChangeDate] DATETIME NULL,
[lastLoginDate] DATETIME NULL,
[emailConfirmedDate] DATETIME NULL,
[invitedDate] DATETIME NULL,
[createDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_createDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[updateDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_updateDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[avatar] NVARCHAR(500) NULL,
[tourData] NTEXT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoUser] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_user] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([id])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoUser_userLogin] ON [umbracoUser] ([userLogin])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoNode] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[uniqueId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_uniqueId] DEFAULT (NEWID()),
[parentId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[level] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[path] NVARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
[sortOrder] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[trashed] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_trashed] DEFAULT ('0'),
[nodeUser] INTEGER NULL,
[text] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[nodeObjectType] UniqueIdentifier NULL,
[createDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_createDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()))
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoNode] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_UniqueId] ON [umbracoNode] ([uniqueId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_ParentId] ON [umbracoNode] ([parentId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_Path] ON [umbracoNode] ([path])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_Trashed] ON [umbracoNode] ([trashed])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_ObjectType] ON [umbracoNode] ([nodeObjectType])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoNode_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([parentId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoNode_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeUser]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

[variations] INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_variations] DEFAULT ('1'))
ALTER TABLE [cmsContentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsContentType] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([pk])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsContentType] ON [cmsContentType] ([nodeId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsContentType_icon] ON [cmsContentType] ([icon])
ALTER TABLE [cmsContentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsContentType_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])
